_sText:
First Hosties Map created.
The Map has Quite a few Unique parts that have never been in a Hostie map Before.
The Map DOES NOT have a Shot for Shot Platform. IT does have a Shot for Shot Hallway that Requires a 3rd Person to Operate. The Switch to the Gun Pit door is Hidden in the walls.
Both of the the Small end walls on the Watch Tower are Breakable.

Featuring:
2 Doors to Terrorist spawn.
2 One way Walls.
1 Rebel Hall and Rebel Door.
1 Gun Toss.
6 Small Cells.
1 White Cell.
1 Unique Trap door Shot for Shot Hall.
1 Gun Pit with Secret Door.
1 Large BreaK Pit.
